OL,6,FNon-food sales growth slowed to 0.7%
OL,7,Fagainst growth of 1.7% last September
OL,8,Fand below the 12-month average growth
OL,9,Fof 0.9%.
OL,11,FOnline non-food sales increased by
OL,12,Fjust 1% against last September's
OL,13,Fgrowth of 3.4% and below the 12-month
OL,14,Faverage growth of 1.8%.
OL,16,FMilder weather meant shoppers delayed
OL,17,Frefreshing autumn and winter
OL,18,Fwardrobes, but electrical sales saw a
OL,19,Fboost due to the release of Apple's
OL,20,Flatest iPhone and watch.
