OL,3,CRetail spending slows as Budget looms
OL,4,Clarge
OL,6,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "With the Budget looming large,
OL,8,Fand households facing higher bills,
OL,9,Fretail spending rose more slowly than
OL,10,Fin recent months.
OL,12,F"Rising inflation and a potentially
OL,13,Ftaxing Budget is weighing on the minds
OL,14,Fof many households planning their
OL,15,FChristmas spending.
OL,17,F"Retailers also face difficult
OL,18,Fdecisions about investment and hiring
OL,19,Fover the golden quarter given
OL,20,Funcertainty over business rates bills
OL,21,Farriving in April.
