OL,3,CRetail spending slows as Budget looms
OL,4,Clarge
OL,6,F"The future of many large anchor
OL,7,Fstores and thousands of jobs remains
OL,8,Fin jeopardy while the Treasury keeps
OL,9,Fthe risk of a new business rates
OL,10,Fsurtax on the table.
OL,12,F"By exempting these shops when the
OL,13,FBudget announcements are made, the
OL,14,FChancellor can reduce the inflationary
OL,15,Fpressures hammering businesses and
OL,16,Fhouseholds alike."
