OL,6,F"As we enter the 'golden quarter' for
OL,7,Fthe sector, retailers are planning
OL,8,Fproduct ranges and promotions to try
OL,9,Fand increase that rate of sales growth.
OL,11,F"They are also mindful that the Budget
OL,12,Fis beginning to move into view, with
OL,13,Frelated detail about business rates
OL,14,Freform and a general need for a boost
OL,15,Fto consumer confidence."
OL,17,FSeparate figures from Barclays show
OL,18,Fconsumer card spending was down by
OL,19,F0.7% year on year in September, a
OL,20,Fsignificant drop from the 0.5% growth
OL,21,Frecorded in August.
